{"tid":1544173,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"醫學會前會長蔡堅：影響全民健康都唔出聲，係咪要收檔？","createTime":"2019-09-05T12:49:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T17:08:43.000Z","uid":86402,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5057c61222f0716ff4bdc84549d4e61edc7e7f0a","tid":1544173,"uid":86402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:49:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/23233/%E8%94%A1%E5%A0%85-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%86%AB%E5%AD%B8%E6%9C%83-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F-23310/%E8%94%A1%E5%A0%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F23233%2F%25E8%2594%25A1%25E5%25A0%2585-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2586%25AB%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%259C%2583-%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F-23310%2F%25E8%2594%25A1%25E5%25A0%2585&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWI%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=12a477db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/23233/%E8%94%A1%E5%A0%85-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%86%AB%E5%AD%B8%E6%9C%83-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F-23310/%E8%94%A1%E5%A0%85</a><br />\n<br />\n太長 自己入去睇<br />\n<br />\n主要講醫學會點被統戰、年輕醫生不信任醫學會"},{"pid":"9736ba02167a7d9d859faec3e9b5b7063cc925ec","tid":1544173,"uid":9049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:52:01.000Z","msg":"各地區連儂牆要人，文宣大量要人<br />\n解釋清楚！！！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全民抗爭，長久戰、拖垮邪惡、打倒腐敗<br />\n<br />\n每日任務：<br />\n1. 抵制支持「邪惡」「無良」的商店，例如cctvb廣告、黨鐵商埸、黑社會、打壓員工的店鋪，減少淘寶、減少使用八達通<br />\n2. 安全情況下跳閘，免費搭港鐵<br />\n3. 夜晚十點咆哮！！！<br />\n4. 做運動，身體健康，鬥長命<br />\n4. 每日一個post，社交媒體戰（Twitter, IG, Facebook, Reddit) #HongKongProtest<br />\n#FreeHongKong #HongKongProtests #Chinazi<br />\nTwitter 共識頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWI%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=5d5b1727\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n5. 不要說推，試著將呢段訊息copy and paste嚟推post<br />\n<br />\n每星期任務：<br />\n1. 罷買Bye Buy Day：星期日、星期五(唔買非必需品）<br />\n2. 每星期做孝子，關心下老母老豆老人家，自己老母自己救<br />\n3. 每星期去連儂牆貼3張文宣<br />\n<br />\n每月任務：<br />\n1. 出糧換美金、買美股、少掂中港股票<br />\n2. MPF都買美股<br />\n3. 搵多幾個人參與<br />\n或者做唔足，但我會堅持到尾，Best effort，你呢？<br />\nVersion 2019.09.05"},{"pid":"07eb2c34a6c563c40173215fcf5f33d59e31fc8a","tid":1544173,"uid":250979,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:52:35.000Z","msg":"蔡醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9679e70e6b2edfdabeb5e40db62e30597f40b28d","tid":1544173,"uid":222513,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"5057c61222f0716ff4bdc84549d4e61edc7e7f0a","tid":1544173,"uid":86402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:49:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/23233/%E8%94%A1%E5%A0%85-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%86%AB%E5%AD%B8%E6%9C%83-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F-23310/%E8%94%A1%E5%A0%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F23233%2F%25E8%2594%25A1%25E5%25A0%2585-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2586%25AB%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%259C%2583-%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F-23310%2F%25E8%2594%25A1%25E5%25A0%2585&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWI%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=12a477db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/23233/%E8%94%A1%E5%A0%85-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%86%AB%E5%AD%B8%E6%9C%83-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F-23310/%E8%94%A1%E5%A0%85</a><br />\n<br />\n太長 自己入去睇<br />\n<br />\n主要講醫學會點被統戰、年輕醫生不信任醫學會"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:52:39.000Z","msg":"我quote 啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「老一輩好多出名醫生，有樓、有車、有老婆仔女，覺得後生仔出來示威，阻礙佢哋日常生活，接受唔到掟石、掟汽油彈，但沒考慮到始作俑者係林鄭，只一味怪責小朋友唔啱。佢哋冇可能唔明白送中條例的壞處，但可能佢哋有外國護照，唔想收成期被人阻住晒，就選擇唔出聲。有些取了政協銜頭的，就更加唔會反政府。」"},{"pid":"c28f18e89c6525f5a4a7b3d00dfbf379c5c9f8d0","tid":1544173,"uid":222513,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:53:36.000Z","msg":"連登就有人話：醫學會入面有鬼，會將個登記名單送去警局，話上急救堂分分鐘被人拉，叫人唔好去。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n70歲都睇連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af4e90e099788ca3694ea3e7e39a5355bf0240fc","tid":1544173,"uid":49853,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:54:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/23233/%E8%94%A1%E5%A0%85-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%86%AB%E5%AD%B8%E6%9C%83-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F-23310/%E8%94%A1%E5%A0%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F23233%2F%25E8%2594%25A1%25E5%25A0%2585-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2586%25AB%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%259C%2583-%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F-23310%2F%25E8%2594%25A1%25E5%25A0%2585&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWI%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=12a477db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/23233/%E8%94%A1%E5%A0%85-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%86%AB%E5%AD%B8%E6%9C%83-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F-23310/%E8%94%A1%E5%A0%85</a><br />\n<br />\n太長 自己入去睇<br />\n<br />\n主要講醫學會點被統戰、年輕醫生不信任醫學會</blockquote>我quote 啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「老一輩好多出名醫生，有樓、有車、有老婆仔女，覺得後生仔出來示威，阻礙佢哋日常生活，接受唔到掟石、掟汽油彈，但沒考慮到始作俑者係林鄭，只一味怪責小朋友唔啱。佢哋冇可能唔明白送中條例的壞處，但可能佢哋有外國護照，唔想收成期被人阻住晒，就選擇唔出聲。<span style=\"color: red;\">有些取了政協銜頭的，就更加唔會反政府。</span>」</blockquote><br />\n高永文<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e8a8f0233bfad33e966ce03cb0b2409f9d35141","tid":1544173,"uid":222513,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:55:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n蔡醫生要長命百歲睇到香港贏嗰日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4f506547530fa46defce2ee76166d751e2e29f","tid":1544173,"uid":222513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"af4e90e099788ca3694ea3e7e39a5355bf0240fc","tid":1544173,"uid":49853,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:54:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/23233/%E8%94%A1%E5%A0%85-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%86%AB%E5%AD%B8%E6%9C%83-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F-23310/%E8%94%A1%E5%A0%85\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F23233%2F%25E8%2594%25A1%25E5%25A0%2585-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%2586%25AB%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E6%259C%2583-%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%2594%259F-23310%2F%25E8%2594%25A1%25E5%25A0%2585&d=t4s0zgtGzRvDs5iH%2BzYNWI%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=12a477db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/23233/%E8%94%A1%E5%A0%85-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E9%86%AB%E5%AD%B8%E6%9C%83-%E9%86%AB%E7%94%9F-23310/%E8%94%A1%E5%A0%85</a><br />\n<br />\n太長 自己入去睇<br />\n<br />\n主要講醫學會點被統戰、年輕醫生不信任醫學會</blockquote>我quote 啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「老一輩好多出名醫生，有樓、有車、有老婆仔女，覺得後生仔出來示威，阻礙佢哋日常生活，接受唔到掟石、掟汽油彈，但沒考慮到始作俑者係林鄭，只一味怪責小朋友唔啱。佢哋冇可能唔明白送中條例的壞處，但可能佢哋有外國護照，唔想收成期被人阻住晒，就選擇唔出聲。<span style=\"color: red;\">有些取了政協銜頭的，就更加唔會反政府。</span>」</blockquote><br />\n高永文<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:56:35.000Z","msg":"佢會被世人唾棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e97546ff58ceb3502190d6ce69dc7f4f98397df6","tid":1544173,"uid":67006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:59:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4528508d3bdbcd550bdfcc02d9086b740bbcf1","tid":1544173,"uid":212626,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:00:17.000Z","msg":"「至於警察，我向來都唔係好信任，ICAC未成立時，我記得去差館被人伸手問攞錢。大約20年前，我被黑社會扑到玻璃樽入眼，20年後都未查到邊個做，雖然大家心中有數。近日的種種事件，令人覺得警隊的系統性有一定缺憾，最高級控制唔到低級、市民不信任，將來，係會有後果。」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n「我七張了，個人一定有慚愧，老海鮮對青年人，是有一定程度的佩服，但我唔覺得需要攬炒，寧願儲足經驗，生命是寶貴的。」<br />\n<br />\n「我們這一代人，被英國佬賣豬仔，當年也想不到可以做什麼，以為一國兩制就係the best deal，希望共產黨堅守承諾，但事實係佢擺明唔要你香港有自主權，要插手入來控制晒。我哋係有一定程度憤怒，但老一輩缺乏勇氣和行動力去做。」"},{"pid":"7bda29d1953acb04320430d6e1d6402a248c97b1","tid":1544173,"uid":128489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:05:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c32b9703e472b9e3273a00901a755c60c908e701","tid":1544173,"uid":156547,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:07:30.000Z","msg":"「似乎有些人淨係掛住支持高牆，忘記雞蛋、忘記在一些立場上不應畏縮。Desmond Tutu（南非聖公會前大主教、諾貝爾和平獎得主圖圖） 說過：『當你在不公義的情況下保持中立，你如同站在壓迫者那一邊。 』（If you are neutral in situations of injustice, you have chosen the side of the oppressor. ）如果唔敢出聲，不如解散個會董會啦。」<br />\n<br />\n「係呀，想當年，大家都係攞全A先入到醫學院，點解而家咁畏縮，唔敢講嘢？醫學會係要帶領業界，你龜縮又兩頭唔到岸，夠膽你咪去支持林鄭囉，但你又唔係，又唔支持市民，企中間做騎牆。（佢想無立場？）係啦，但個會宗旨係維護民康，你見有人被打到盲，難道這些都不是民康？」<br />\n<br />\n「我可以做的，係買地鐵飛、麥當勞劵給小朋友，心底裡小小的支持。希望你哋，唔好餓親。」<br />\n<br />\n蔡醫生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0af62bb20f540cbb78c49030194f231ded7e72f","tid":1544173,"uid":124410,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:11:28.000Z","msg":"「我可以做的，係買地鐵飛、麥當勞劵給小朋友，心底裡小小的支持。希望你哋，唔好餓親。」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d345ce28abef7716d2edd63784c9375d2720f72c","tid":1544173,"uid":197178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:20:09.000Z","msg":"有風骨"},{"pid":"fa545df4c8ec36621de686a2a56e7d5afb449a2c","tid":1544173,"uid":58335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:42:16.000Z","msg":"上醫醫國 中醫醫人 下醫醫病<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個班下醫都唔知叫唔叫好<br />\n可能直頭叫庸醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"658418ace082e842c253d488bbf670287fae700c","tid":1544173,"uid":53612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:48:14.000Z","msg":"當你在不公義的情況下保持中立，你如同站在壓迫者那一邊。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">中立者 是幫兇</span></span>"},{"pid":"e3f9c75ee9db7002893f81d6f73a190cdf72da61","tid":1544173,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T13:58:57.000Z","msg":"其實年輕醫生可唔可以考慮自立一個會出黎？<br />\n唔使睇呢班人面色<br />\n好似教協同教聯咁"},{"pid":"f30286bce33110233856f21a77e77741577e1201","tid":1544173,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T14:43:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2f77cd95067f1cbb8826db9bc469c4da945518cf","tid":1544173,"uid":86402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e8a8f0233bfad33e966ce03cb0b2409f9d35141","tid":1544173,"uid":222513,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T12:55:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n蔡醫生要長命百歲睇到香港贏嗰日<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:12:46.000Z","msg":"希望今年就睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2b20025b00005d8090888c47d96ff88d642cbd2","tid":1544173,"uid":222513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:08:22.000Z","msg":"直資偏藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同情daddy間錶舖今個月賺少咗"},{"pid":"343b54b4be6fdaaf9d4c4b675c0e25a4a614d074","tid":1544173,"uid":222513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c2b20025b00005d8090888c47d96ff88d642cbd2","tid":1544173,"uid":222513,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:08:22.000Z","msg":"直資偏藍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同情daddy間錶舖今個月賺少咗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T17:08:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />覆錯"}]}